---
title: "invalidateOrders (GPV2CompatibleAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_role: caller has ORDER_MANAGER_ROLE
    q_check_role --> q_iter: role check passed
    q_check_role --> q_revert: missing role
    q_revert --> [*]: revert AccessControl error
    q_iter --> q_invalidate: i < orderUids.length
    q_iter --> [*]: i >= orderUids.length (loop done)
    q_invalidate --> q_iter: i_gpV2Settlement.invalidateOrder(orderUids[i]); i++

    note right of q_invalidate
        INV-001: Only ORDER_MANAGER_ROLE can invalidate orders
        INV-002: Delegates to GPv2Settlement.invalidateOrder for each UID
        INV-003: Invalidated orders will fail isValidSignature hash check on settlement
    end note
